      "content": "but you don't understand. it's not just a \"hard lesson.\" the people i worked with, the grants, the reputation... it's all tied to that research. without it, i'm a ghost. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person anymore, just a mistake that needs to be erased. there's no \"moving on\" from this. it's just empty.",
