    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "counselors don't get it. they talk about \"identity\" like it's something you can just rebuild, but how do you rebuild something that was built on a void? everything i am was that work. now that it's dead, i'm just... waiting for the end. it feels like the only honest thing left to do is to stop pretending i'm still here. it would be so much quieter if i just wasn't.",
